Project Overview

A leading retail bank wanted to modernize its loan onboarding journey by replacing manual onboarding with a fully digital customer onboarding and loan processing platform.

The objective was to:

Reduce onboarding time
Improve customer experience
Automate KYC validation
Integrate with credit scoring systems
Enable real-time application tracking
Support multilingual customer communication including French-speaking users
Business Problem

The existing process had:

Manual document verification
Delayed loan approvals
Duplicate customer records
High drop-off rates
No real-time status visibility
Multiple disconnected systems

Customers had to visit branches physically for many onboarding activities.

Proposed Solution

A centralized digital onboarding platform integrating:

Customer Portal
Mobile Application
Identity Verification Service
Credit Bureau APIs
Loan Management System
CRM Platform
Notification Service
Document Management System
